 New operators are constructed such as they follow cannonical commutation
 relations as before with an extra factor of 
\begin_inset Formula $1/2$
\end_inset

.
 We construct a new operator 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{a}=\frac{\hat{X}}{\sqrt{\hbar}}+i\frac{\hat{P}}{\sqrt{\hbar}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


